    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Imaginary species of sea serpent, derived from the Latin vulgate of a passage in Isaiah. Also generic, imaginary sea creatures who are part woman, including the Sirens of Classical mythology.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
